Time::Piece::DB2
==================

Time::Piece::DB2, when used, adds several DB2-specific methods to
the Time::Piece class.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module won't do much without Time::Piece!

